title: Ukrainian military had 67 combat engagements with Russian forces near Bilohorivka, Zolotarivka of Luhansk region and Yampoliv...
content: Ukrainian military had 67 combat engagements with Russian forces near Bilohorivka, Zolotarivka of Luhansk region and Yampolivka, Terny, Rozdolivka, Vesele of Donetsk region, Bohdanivka, Ivanivske, Klischiyivka of Donetsk region, Berdychi, Semenivka, Tonenke, Pervomayske, Netaylove, Nevelske of Donetsk region, Krasnohorivka, Heorhiyivka, Novomykhaylivka, Vodyane, Urozhayne, Staromayorske of Donetsk region and Robotyne of Zaporizhzhia region, at the eastern bank of Dnipro river in Kherson region, - General Staff of Armed Forces of Ukraine says in the evening report
